<figureCitation id="FA4615716915F9BBBD89EBDB451ABC9D" captionStart="Figure 9" captionStartId="F9" captionText="Figure 9. Hebeloma colvinii A HK 16.005, photograph H. Knudsen B distribution of cited collections; C spores x 1600 and D cheilocystidia x 1000 of HK 16.005 in Melzer's reagent. Scale bars: 5 µm; microphotographs H. K. J. Beker." figureDoi="10.3897/mycokeys.79.63363.figure9" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/533400" pageId="0" pageNumber="17">Fig. 9</figureCitation>
</paragraph>
